Embedded JavaScript

It is a template engine used with Node.js to generate HTML markup with JavaScript.
It allows you to insert JavaScript code into HTML to create dynamic web pages.
Example:
    Instagram pages,
        Google's page,
        Amazon's page,
        Mera bhi account page h,
        All have the same structure.

Use Cases:
    Displaying data from the backend.
    Reusing HTML components.

Installation:
    npm i ejs